=\"_blank\" href=\"https://youtu.be/pExPIfVbMh4?si=q1damVOxu5a6-omy\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><strong>Cartoon City Free</strong></a><strong> </strong>- pack demonstration</p><p></p><p><span class=\"fabkit-prose-color--yellow\">▶️<strong> Key Features </strong>◀️</span></p><p><span><strong>●</strong> <strong>80 models.</strong> Buildings, cars, roads, and various city props, allowing you to create your own city-themed game.</span></p><p><span><strong>● Demo scene</strong> is a prepared location that you can view in pictures, ready for use in your projects and will save your precious time. You can use it or create your own unique level.</span></p><p><span><strong>●</strong> <strong>Models are optimized</strong> for game engines, easily editable and customizable. You can also use them for animations, advertising and marketing, VR/AR.</span></p><p><strong>●</strong> <strong>Support.</strong> Free updates and <span>technical support available in our </span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://discord.com/invite/jxrQM8hXnd\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span><strong>Discord</strong></span></a><span>.</span></p><p></p><p><span class=\"fabkit-prose-color--yellow\">▶️<strong> Pack Content </strong>◀️</span></p><p><span><strong>Demo scene</strong> is a prepared location that you can view in pictures.</span></p><p><span><br><strong>80 models:</strong></span></p><p><span><strong>● Buildings (x4)</strong></span></p><p><span>Eco Building Grid, Eco Building Slope, Eco Building Terrace, Regular Building Twisted Tower Large.</span></p><p><span><strong>● Cars (x6)</strong></span></p><p><span>Delivery van, sedan, hatchback, sports car, classic car.</span></p><p><span><strong>● Roads (x7)</strong></span></p><p><span>Straight and curved road segments, intersections, T-junctions, multi-lane and single-lane sections, turning pieces.</span></p><p><span><strong>● Sidewalks (x5)</strong></span></p><p><span>Straight sections, corner sections, paved areas with curbs, paved areas without curbs, paved areas with green strips.</span></p><p><span><strong>● Vegetation (x3)</strong></span></p><p><span>Palm, Bush.</span></p><p><span><strong>● Billboards (x5)</strong></span></p><p><span>Park ad, gaming console ad, hanging banner, digital text board, digital landscape board.</span></p><p><span><strong>● Props (x18)</strong></span></p><p><span>Fountain, traffic lights, street lights, bus stop, trash bins, dumpsters, recycling containers, graffiti sign.</span></p><p><span>* Some objects consist of multiple models, so the total number of assets and the number of assets in the categories differ.</span></p><p></p><p><span><strong>Check out more packs from our Free Collection.</strong></span></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fab.com/listings/0c8f3917-2461-4775-a853-b995bb93bac5\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span><strong>Animals Free</strong></span></a></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fab.com/listings/94fd60a2-5659-4fc4-af1d-a8cdd2681c2e\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span><strong>Creative Characters Free</strong></span></a></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fab.com/listings/e5d17709-8ebe-44af-946f-5991117095bc\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span><strong>Fantasy Free</strong></span></a></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fab.com/listings/3eca0616-aa73-4348-9af5-cb4c173f237e\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span><strong>Furniture Free</strong></span></a></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fab.com/listings/be36701c-890c-40b7-bd91-10919327f66f\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span><strong>Military Free</strong></span></a></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fab.com/listings/9939041c-a505-47f5-a636-ee51381787ea\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span><strong>Weapons Free</strong></span></a></p><p></p><h5><span class=\"fabkit-prose-color--yellow\"><strong>▶️&nbsp;Support</strong></span><strong> </strong><span class=\"fabkit-prose-color--y